## Code Review Workflow

```bash
/code-review [ticket-number]
```

Reviews all tickets in "in-review" status or a specific ticket.

---

## Pair Programming

```bash
/pair 5        # Work on ticket #5
```

Learning modes: Guided, Collaborative, Exploratory, Watch & Learn.

